message 'APR and APU are used by Apache 2 spells'
message 'Do *not* select APR 1.0 if you plan to use apache2 spell (HTTPD 2.0)'
config_query APR_BRANCH_0_9 'Would you like to use APR 0.9 for HTTPD 2.0.x (APR 1.0 otherwise)?' y
config_query APR_CHECKOUT   'Would you like to use the latest source code that may not build?'   n
